---
title: Grilled Shawarma-Spiced Chicken Fattoush with Fresh Salad and Grilled Pita Chips
description: Aromatic shawarma-spiced chicken thighs are perfect for grilling and catching all that smoky BBQ flavour. A Levantine-inspired fattoush salad with crispy, crunchy pita chips, fresh veggies and a bright lemony dressing brings layer of texture and flavour to the table. What more could you ask for in a summer dinner?
